This is a little random, but have you ever heard of a Japanese word game called 'shiritori' Gura? It's like where one person says 'apple," the other says 'egg,' the first says 'green;' you have to think of a word that starts with the last letter of the previous word. You responding to Japanese words with different ones that sound similar made me think of it, but maybe it would actually be a fun way to help memorize Japanese words!
